high_descs: Move forward and go to the front of the black end table on the right.
Pick up the wrist watch on the top of the end table.
Turn around go to the left front corner of the dining table.
Place the wrist watch on the white plate on the table.
Pick up the white plate with the wrist watch on it.
Go around the dining table past the sofa to the glass coffee table.
Place the plate with the wrist watch on it on the middle shelf of the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the white plate with a wrist watch to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the black table against the wall on your right.
Pick up the watch off of the black table.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right to face the glass table.
Put the watch on the white plate that is on the corner of the glass table.
Pick up the white plate with the watch on it off of the glass table.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a right and walk around the black couch to the glass coffee table.
Put the white plate with the watch on it on the middle shelf of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a white plate with a watch on it on a coffee table shelf.

high_descs: Go forward and turn to the right to face the black table.
Pick the watch up from the black table.
Turn around and face the glass table behind.
Put the watch down on the white plate on the table.
Pick the white plate up from the table.
Cross the room and turn to the right to face the glass table in front of the couch.
Put the plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a watch on it on a table.
